Meme: a fast mind-mapping tool
(c) 2010 Jamie Webb - MIT license

Requires:

- Python 2.6
- PyGTK 2.22

To install:

  make && sudo make install

To run:

  meme

Keyboard reference:

  Up/Down     Move between nodes at the current nexting level
  Left/Right  Move between nesting levels
  Home        Go to the root node
  Enter       Add a new sibling below the selected node
  Tab         Add a new child of the selected node
  Insert      Edit the text of the selected node
  Space       Collaspe/Expand the selected node

Or, just start typing to replace the text of the current node.

While editing, press Enter/Tab/Up/Down to finish, or Escape to abort.
